Module fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp
Package fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp

Class CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp.CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse
public class CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse extends Object
The `CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse` class represents the One Call API 3.0 response. It contains the latitude, longitude, timezone, timezone offset, current weather data, minute forecast for the next hour, hourly forecast for the next 48 hours, daily forecast for the next 8 days, and government weather alerts.
Since:
2023-12-06
Version:

Author:
